quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,"This is a chapter which We have revealed and which We have made obligatory; We have sent down clear revelations in it, so that you may take heed"
  24,2,"Flog the adulteress and the adulterer, each one of them, with a hundred lashes. Let no pity for them cause you to disobey God, if you truly believe in God and the Last Day; and let their punishment be witnessed by a number of believers"
  24,3,"The adulterer shall marry only an adulteress or a polytheist woman, and an adulteress shall marry only an adulterer or a polytheist man; such marriages are forbidden for believers"
  24,4,"Those who defame chaste women, but cannot produce four witnesses, shall be given eighty lashes. Do not accept their testimony ever after, for they are transgressors"
  24,5,"save those who afterwards repent and make amends, for truly God is forgiving and merciful"
  24,6,One who accuses his wife and has no witnesses except himself shall swear four times by God that his charge is true
  24,7,"and the fifth time, that God's curse may be upon him if he is telling a lie"
  24,8,"The wife shall receive no punishment, if she bears witness four times in the name of God that her husband has lied"
  24,9,"and, a fifth time that God's wrath will be upon her if he is telling the truth"
  24,10,"Were it not for God's grace and His mercy upon you, [you would have come to grief] and God is wise, acceptor of repentance"